Entering edit mode

Incertae sedis indicates the rank associated to the term is of unknown or uncertain classification.

So, for question 1, Clostridiales_Incertae.Sedis.XIII is a family (from the Clostridiales order) of unknown or uncertain classification, for question 2, genus_Erysipelotrichaceae_incertae_sedis is a genus (from the Erysipelotrichaceae family) of unknown or uncertain classification.

