For any positive integer n:
\begin{align} (a+x)^n & = \sum_{k=0}^n \left( \begin{array}{ll}n\\k \end{array}\right) x^k a^{n-k}\\ & = a^n + \binom{n}{1} a^{n-1}x + \binom{n}{2} a^{n-2}x^2 + \binom{n}{3} a^{n-3}x^3 + \ldots + x^n \\ \end{align}
