$\frac {1}{\cosh x} = 1 - {x2 \over 2} + {5x^4 \over 24} -{61x^6 \over 720} + \cdots \frac{(-1)^nE_nx^{2n}}{(2n)!} + \cdots$ $\vert x \vert < {\pi \over 2}$
