• Also, If I run this on the whole file and not just the first 6 lines, after a while, the program fails on TypeError: '<' not supported between instances of 'Bed' and 'Bed'. I'm upgrading cgat to see if the error persists. – bli Aug 10 '17 at 15:45
• I reported the issues here: github.com/CGATOxford/cgat/issues/347 – bli Aug 10 '17 at 16:27
