## Study23 Group Title Okay. I'm having trouble with series. Here's the problem (I'm looking to see whether the series is convergent or divergent, if convergent I have to find the sum it converges to): summation from n=1 to infinity of $$\ \frac{n}{n+5}$$. one year ago one year ago

