A silo is filled to capacity with W pounds of wheat. Rats eat r pounds a day. After 25 days, what percentage of the silo’s capacity have the rats eaten?

A. 25r/W

B. 25r/(100W)

C. 2,500r/W

D. r/W

E. r/(25W)

