40,769
Staff Emeritus
??? Why do the diagonal matrices
$$\begin{bmatrix}1 & 0 \\ 0 & 2\end{bmatrix}$$
and
$$\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 0 & 0 \\ 0 & 2 & 0 \\ 0 & 0 & 3\end{bmatrix}$$
NOT count as "all entries postive"?

8. micromass

19,347
Staff Emeritus
He probably doesn't consider 0 to be positive.

